name: CCTV Player
body:
### Welcome to CCTV Player support page.
CCTV Player is a video-stream player
- this is video only (no audio) player;
- only rtsp ip cameras are currently supported.
- to watch video stream please use connection url from your service provider.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with CCTV Player? [Contact support](alexander.gorskih@gmail.com) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
